Package fluent.ly

Class ___

  • java.lang.Object
    • fluent.ly.___
  • public abstract class ___
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple implementation of design by contract services. Violations are reported to System.err. Error descriptions are passed by a printf like argument syntax. Services are often used with static import.
    Since:
    11/01/2006)
    Author:
    Yossi Gil (
